            p.
                <b>Definition</b> (Induction Principle $ind_2$).
                $$
                    \prod_{C\ :\ 𝟐\ \rightarrow\ U} \prod_{x\ :\ C(0_2)} \prod_{y\ :\ C(0_1)} \prod_{z\ :\ 𝟐} C(z) := ind_2(C,x,y,z).
